                    </p>
                    <a class="buy_now" href="/products">Buy now</a>
                </div>
                <!-- .slid_content -->
                <img src="/img/content/slid-1.png" alt="Slid 1" title="" />
            </li>

            <li>
                <div class="slid_content">
                    <h2 style="color: #744747">Precious Metals</h2>
                    <p style="color: #744747">
                        There’s no gift quite like diamond jewelry. Whether you’re looking for
